    {
      "id": "d3-output",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 80,
      "y": 475,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "roughness": 0,
      "text": "Result: TreeView sidebar shows each skill once with agent badges (e.g. \"Claude, Cursor, Copilot\")",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "createdAt": "2026-03-05T07:53:03.567Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-05T07:53:48.096Z",
      "version": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "d3-ann1-bg",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 940,
      "y": 120,
      "width": 340,
      "height": 190,
      "backgroundColor": "#fff3bf",
      "strokeColor": "#e8590c",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "roundness": {
        "type": 3
      },
      "createdAt": "2026-03-05T07:53:23.000Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-05T07:53:57.891Z",
      "version": 3,
      "groupIds": [
        "mmd65ytaq2sv36a37ag"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "d3-ann1-text",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 955,
      "y": 130,
      "width": 310,
      "strokeColor": "#495057",
      "roughness": 0,
      "text": "Why 22 directories?\n\nProblem: In 2026, developers use 11\ndifferent AI agents. Each stores skills in\nits own folder — global and per-project.\n\nSolution: We maintain a list of all 11\nagents and scan both scopes for each.\nOne extension replaces checking 22\nfolders by hand.",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "createdAt": "2026-03-05T07:53:23.000Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-05T07:53:57.894Z",
      "version": 2,
      "groupIds": [
        "mmd65ytaq2sv36a37ag"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "d3-ann2-bg",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 940,
      "y": 325,
      "width": 340,
      "height": 195,
      "backgroundColor": "#fff3bf",
      "strokeColor": "#e8590c",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "roundness": {
        "type": 3
      },
      "createdAt": "2026-03-05T07:53:23.000Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-05T07:53:58.372Z",
      "version": 4,
      "groupIds": [
        "mmd65z6mbkxr0tkqu6u"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "d3-ann2-text",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 955,
      "y": 335,
      "width": 310,
      "strokeColor": "#495057",
      "roughness": 0,
      "text": "The symlink problem\n\nProblem: Skills are installed as symlinks,\nbut Node.js says symlinks aren't folders.\nA naive scan would miss every skill.\n\nSolution: A helper checks \"is this a\nsymlink?\" first, then follows it to see if\nthe target is a real folder. Two-step\ncheck that works on all platforms.",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "createdAt": "2026-03-05T07:53:23.000Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-05T07:53:58.374Z",
      "version": 3,
      "groupIds": [
        "mmd65z6mbkxr0tkqu6u"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "d3-ann3-bg",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 940,
      "y": 535,
      "width": 340,
      "height": 170,
      "backgroundColor": "#fff3bf",
      "strokeColor": "#e8590c",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "roundness": {
        "type": 3
      },
      "createdAt": "2026-03-05T07:53:23.000Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-05T07:54:09.875Z",
      "version": 4,
      "groupIds": [
        "mmd65zj2582agirmazp"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "d3-ann3-text",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 955,
      "y": 545,
      "width": 310,
      "strokeColor": "#495057",
      "roughness": 0,
      "text": "Why deduplicate?\n\nProblem: The same skill is symlinked\ninto 5+ agent folders. Without dedup,\nthe UI would show 5 copies.\n\nSolution: Group by folder name. Show\nthe skill once with badges listing which\nagents have it (e.g. \"Claude, Cursor\").",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "createdAt": "2026-03-05T07:53:23.000Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-05T07:53:58.822Z",
      "version": 3,
      "groupIds": [
        "mmd65zj2582agirmazp"
      ]
    },
